node.text:
Rainbows clouds over Merritt Island 🌈 🌥

Have you ever seen clouds like this?

Video by Christian Servant Patriot 

Cloud iridescence usually happens in altocumulus, cirrocumulus, lenticular and cirrus clouds. Iridescent clouds happen because of diffraction – a phenomenon that occurs when small water droplets or small ice crystals scatter the sun’s light.

node.text:
🌅 Ever seen a sunset this good?

Oahu is a U.S. island in the Central Pacific, part of the Hawaiian island chain and home to the state capital, Honolulu. Highlights of the city include historic Chinatown and the Punchbowl, a crater-turned-cemetery. Waikiki is an iconic beach, dining and nightlife area. West of Honolulu is Pearl Harbor, site of the WWII's 1941 bombing attack and home to the USS Arizona Memorial.

📽 @kamalugoo 
📍 O’ahu, Hawaii
🎶 ZAYN - Dusk Till Dawn (Radio Edit) (feat. Sia)

node.text:
Adventure calling🌲🌅 Would you visit Finland during the summer?

Photos by @jukkarisikko 

While Finland is usually associated with snow draped mountains and Christmas getaways, it’s definitely worth visiting during the warmer months as well! Escape to the countryside in a lakeside cottage, take on stunning hillside hikes, or stay up all night to enjoy Finland’s midnight sun. 🇫🇮
